<i>...against the Lycans.</i>

13
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,886
<i>And I was good at it.</i>

14
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,289
<i>Then I found Michael Corvin...</i>

15
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,322
<i>...a human that was...</i>

16
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,891
<i>...turned to neither Vampire...</i>

17
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,723
<i>...nor Lycan...</i>

18
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,049
<i>...but a hybrid...</i>

19
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,361
<i>...of the two.</i>

20
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:31,442
<i>Everything changed.</i>

21
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,522
<i>Allies turned...</i>

22
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,488
<i>...enemies...</i>

23
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,285
<i>...and the Vampire elders I had...</i>

24
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,169
<i>...protected for over six centuries...</i>

25
