<i>...wanted me dead.</i>

26
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:45,200
<i>We retaliated...</i>

27
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,401
<i>...killed the elders...</i>

28
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,682
<i>...and for a moment of time...</i>

29
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,442
<i>...we were safe.</i>

30
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,848
<i>But then...</i>

31
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,849
<i>...a new darkness arose.</i>

32
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:03,728
<i>In the nine days...</i>

33
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:06,526
<i>...since the first discovery
of the non-human species...</i>

34
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,648
<i>...scores of so-called “covens“
have been uncovered.</i>

35
00:02:09,760 --> 00:02:12,081
<i>Estimates of the number
of infected have skyrocketed.</i>

36
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,247
<i>Military sources confirm...</i>

37
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,843
<i>...that the primary measures...</i>

38
