have escaped the perimeter...</i>

151
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:40,451
<i>...and are no longer
under Antigen control.</i>

152
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:44,207
<i>Secure the outer gates and use
extreme caution upon encounter.</i>

153
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:47,603
<i>Report immediately upon
coming into contact...</i>

154
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,609
Hey, how did you get in there?

155
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,929
You're not allowed in here.

156
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,125
The pier is closed.

157
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,960
Since when?

158
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:31,171
A long time ago. Come on.

159
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,282
How long?

160
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:37,449
About 12 years ago.

161
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,885
Since the cleansing. Why?

162
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:42,686
You okay, ma'am?

163
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,604
<i>Attention, all units, code three call.</i>

164
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:47,445
<i>Receiving a report of an assault,
Exit 39 underpass.</i>

165
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:51,641
<i>Possible non-human aggressor.
Proceed with caution.</i>

166
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:54,280
