to try to find a cure...

234
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:37,847
...to prevent another outbreak.

235
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,525
You were told that I would...

236
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,409
...lead you to the hybrid. Why?

237
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:44,806
