No.

535
00:51:46,320 --> 00:51:48,527
Because you wouldn't need
a fucking gun to do it.

536
00:51:51,320 --> 00:51:52,207
<i>A few years ago...</i>

537
00:51:52,360 --> 00:51:55,170
