566
00:53:20,560 --> 00:53:21,846
...of your test subject...

567
00:53:22,000 --> 00:53:24,606
...he continues to demonstrate
immunity to silver?

568
00:53:24,760 --> 00:53:26,046
Absolutely.

569
00:53:26,360 --> 00:53:30,445
