you did an excellent job.

585
00:54:08,000 --> 00:54:10,048
Saving the lives of thousands.

586
00:54:11,040 --> 00:54:12,963
What are you talking about?

587
00:54:13,120 --> 00:54:15,487
An entire species
saved from extinction.

588
00:54:21,200 --> 00:54:22,326
Jacob.

589
00:55:05,400 --> 00:55:09,246
After today, you won't have to
wait so long between injections.

590
00:55:09,840 --> 00:55:11,808
Are you sure she's ready?

591
00:55:11,960 --> 00:55:13,644
Oestrogen levels high...

592
00:55:13,800 --> 00:55:16,770
...intervals between menses
holding steady.

593
00:55:16,960 --> 00:55:18,849
It's come of age.

594
00:55:19,560 --> 00:55:22,803
Everything's worked out
just as we'd hoped.

595
00:55:26,560 --> 00:55:28,483
You're the first proof of it.

596
00:55:30,240 --> 00:55:31,924
I'm proud of you, son.

597
00:55:36,480 --> 00:55:38,209
Now that it's with us again...

598
00:55:38,360 --> 00:55:41,409
...we'll have all the genetic material
we need, ready for cloning.

599
00:55:41,560 --> 00:55:44,928
Enough to produce
an endless supply of vaccine.

600
00:55:46,040 --> 00:55:46,882
Imagine.

601
00:55:47,440 --> 00:55:50,171
Our species immune to silver.

602
00:55:50,320 --> 00:55:51,924
No more hiding.

603
00:55:52,080 --> 00:55:55,402
Every Lycan under our command
as powerful as you are.

604
00:55:56,200 --> 00:55:58,680
I've even begun injecting myself.

605
00:55:59,320 --> 00:56:01,800
I only wish Mother
were here to see it.

606
