608
00:56:10,720 --> 00:56:12,404
Remember that.

609
00:56:25,880 --> 00:56:27,405
Of course, Father.

610
00:56:34,360 --> 00:56:35,009
Look...

611
00:56:35,160 --> 00:56:39,085
...if you're right about Antigen, who
knows how many Lycans will be there?

612
00:56:39,440 --> 00:56:42,046
