I can help you.

615
00:56:48,000 --> 00:56:50,526
- Why?
- Just tell me what your plan is.

616
00:57:14,160 --> 00:57:16,128
It's worse if you try to fight it.

617
00:57:17,240 --> 00:57:18,446
Trust me.

618
00:57:20,840 --> 00:57:22,365
