620
00:57:26,680 --> 00:57:28,250
It was a gift.

621
00:57:29,200 --> 00:57:31,168
From a man named
Alexander Corvinus.

622
00:57:32,120 --> 00:57:33,451
The founding father.

623
00:57:37,240 --> 00:57:39,641
