We lived like that for a few years.

626
00:57:51,000 --> 00:57:52,604
Then came the Purge.

627
00:57:54,000 --> 00:57:57,607
The feds were conducting door-to-doors
and when they knocked on ours...

628
00:58:03,120 --> 00:58:05,691
...well, she told me she loved me...

629
00:58:07,480 --> 00:58:09,642
